9 (b) Public entities may pool together to purchase casualty insurance, property
10 insurance, or health insurance or to self–insure against casualty, property, or health risks.
11 Article – Local Government
12 22–101.
13 (a) In this title the following words have the meanings indicated.
14 (g) “Resilience Authority” means an authority incorporated by one or more local
15 governments in accordance with this title whose purpose is to undertake or support
16 resilience infrastructure projects.
17 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
18 October 1, 2025.

